- `terminedia` PyPI: https://pypi.org/project/terminedia/
- `termgl` PyPI: https://pypi.org/project/termgl/
- `chafa.py` PyPI: https://pypi.org/project/chafa.py/
- Chafa man page (symbol classes, font ratio concepts): https://hpjansson.org/chafa/man/
- `rot.js` (terminal backend / `layout:"term"`): https://github.com/ondras/rot.js and https://www.npmjs.com/package/rot-js
